com.att.research.xacml.util

Class XACMLPolicyScanner

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.research.xacml.util.XACMLPolicyScanner

  • public class XACMLPolicyScanner
extends java.lang.Object
    class XACMLPolicyScanner This class traverses the hierarchy of a XACML 3.0 policy. You can optionally pass a Callback class and override any desired methods to retrieve information from a policy.
    Author:
    pameladragosh
